  ROLLER SKATE:
  <br/>
  To sign "skate," form your hands into "bent V" handshapes.  Then put them 
  in front of you, palms facing up. 
  Alternate moving them forward and back a couple times.  
  Memory tip:  Think of the movement of a skater's feet.
  <br/>
