  <br/>
  To sign SKATE as in I-C-E "SKATE"  form your hands into "X" 
  handshapes.   Then put them in front of you, palms facing up. 
  Alternate moving them forward and back a couple times.
  <br/>
  Memory tip:  Think of the movement of a skater's feet. Think of the 
	upturned "X" as representing the curved blade on the skates.
 </p>
